history.content:
Do you want to ace your interviews? Want to make yourself stand out among thousands of others?

 

IEEE will be holding an Interview Prep Workshop on Thursday 4/15 at 8PM PDT with Orkun Duman, a software engineer at Google with experience at Apple and Microsoft as well! Our speaker will talk about the general interview process and will help you identify key points during technical and verbal interviews.

 

If you would like to attend the Interview Prep Workshop, please sign up at: 

http://bit.ly/interview-prep-signup

 

Zoom Link:  

http://bit.ly/interview-ieee

See you at Interview Prep!
